01:51:12.907 --> 01:51:15.276
Animal.

1221
01:51:28.890 --> 01:51:29.999
Oh.

1222
01:51:30.000 --> 01:51:32.192
Oh.

1223
01:51:32.193 --> 01:51:34.395
Oh.

1224
01:51:36.264 --> 01:51:41.935
- Oh.
- I'm going out. I'll send for a wagon.

1225
01:51:41.936 --> 01:51:45.539
Howard. Howard!

1226
