Wake up. Buglar. Baby!

1227
01:51:48.910 --> 01:51:52.012
Come on. sweetheart.
Wake up! Wake up!

1228
01:51:52.013 --> 01:51:54.014
Oh!

1229
01:51:54.015 --> 01:51:56.149
I beg your pardon.

1230
01:51:56.150 --> 01:51:59.999
Sethe. you take my armload
