you think sayin' good-bye
is gonna break me into pieces?

1260
01:54:00.000 --> 01:54:02.577
You think sayin' good-bye
is gonna break me into pieces?

1261
01:54:09.383 --> 01:54:12.253
You're a sweet man.

1262
01:54:26.133 --> 01:54:29.070
So long. Paul d.

1263
